description:
NEA Jazz Master and 2015 GRAMMY nominee, Bobby Hutcherson, welcomes us in his home and takes us through his day.  In this episode, Bobby takes us to the beach and talks to us about his move from New York City to San Francisco, which is where he met his wife, Rosemary.

Subscribe to our channel http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCP108sGgYT_TlG2YRColGcg?sub_confirmation=1

Check back next week for part two of this NIGHT IN THE LIFE with BOBBY HUTCHERSON. 

To learn more about Jazz at Lincoln Center, visit us at http://www.jazz.org
title: A NIGHT IN THE LIFE: Bobby Hutcherson (PART ONE)
